## URL Redirect Strategy (No Bitly Needed)
Using Cloudflare Worker `/go/` redirects with UTM parameters baked in.
- Clean branded URLs for ads: `paradisesurfsidesc.com/go/facebook-summer`
- Redirects to destination with UTMs: `/?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=paid&utm_campaign=summer2026`
- Server-side click logging in Cloudflare + GA4 campaign attribution

Live slugs (in `worker/index.js`):
```
/go/facebook-summer  → /?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=paid&utm_campaign=summer2026
/go/facebook-pool    → /?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=paid&utm_campaign=pool-feature
/go/instagram        → /?utm_source=instagram&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=organic
/go/email-april      → /?utm_source=email&utm_medium=newsletter&utm_campaign=april2026
/go/book             → [booking URL with UTMs]
/go/guest            → /guest/?utm_source=qr&utm_medium=print&utm_campaign=in-property
```

